data.description: This spacious 4 bedroom 2 bathroom house is everything and more! This home sits on a beautiful corner lot in the highly sought after North Magness Creek Subdivision. The open floor plan is perfect for large or growing families! Newly renovated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances including a gas stove, dishwasher, and many safety features! New paint, light fixtures, and new quartz island countertop! New LVP flooring throughout downstairs! 3 bedrooms, including the Master, is on one level with a cozy guest room/ office upstairs! The large backyard is a beautiful escape with so much potential for night life and hosting! Schedule your showing TODAY!
